Name: Dunkley
Description:
The Division of Dunkley consists of:

  • Frankston City Council, and
  • part of the Mornington Peninsula Shire Council.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of Louisa Margaret Dunkley, 1866-1927. Dunkley was a union leader and feminist who founded the Victorian Women's Post and Telegraph Association in 1900 and campaigned for equal pay for women.
